<h2 class="bold font-l">Tesla Trooper</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Heavily-armored, lightning-shooting bruisers who can go toe-to-toe with enemy tanks. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="lausp0" data-video-descrip="Insulated, lightly armored vessels armed with electrifying Tesla weapons. Can clamber ashore." data-video-title="Stingray" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/lausp0_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/lausp0.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/LightningGun" data-video-tropename="Lightning Gun" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="VideoGame/CommandAndConquerRedAlertSeries,VideoGame/CommandAndConquer,VideoGame/CommandAndConquerRedAlert3" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/lausp0.jpg">
